# English Only

All user-facing text and AI-generated content in this project **must be in English**.

## UI copy

- Every visible string goes in `src/lib/labels.ts` — no hardcoded UI text in components or pages
- No Indonesian (or other language) labels, placeholders, buttons, headings, or error messages
- Level names use English keys in `labels.levels` (`Basic`, `Intermediate`, `Advanced`)

## Ollama / AI

- System prompts in `src/lib/ollama.ts` must instruct the model to respond in **English**
- Quiz feedback prompts (`buildFeedbackPrompt`) must be written in English
- Chat route (`src/app/api/ai/chat/route.ts`) must use `CHAT_SYSTEM_PROMPT` from `lib/ollama.ts`
- AI fallback messages (when generation fails) must be in English

## Seed & sample content

- Default titles, descriptions, and demo content in `prisma/seed.ts` or migrations should be English

## When adding features

1. Add new strings to `labels.ts` first
2. Import `labels` in the component — never inline copy
3. For new AI endpoints, reuse or extend English prompts in `lib/ollama.ts`
